text.section:
A duly licensed manufacturer, distributor, or wholesaler may sell or distribute controlled substances, other than samples, to any of the following persons:
To a manufacturer, wholesaler, or pharmacy;
To a practitioner;
To the administrator in charge of a hospital, but only for use by or in that hospital;
To a person in charge of a laboratory, but only for use in that laboratory for scientific and medical research purposes;
To a person registered pursuant to the federal controlled substances laws.
